===Noun===
{{en-noun-irreg|knives}}

# A [[utensil]] consisting of a [[sharpen]]ed piece of hard material, usually steel or other [[metal]], but possibly [[ceramic]], [[plastic]], [[glass]] or [[stone]], usually attached to a [[handle]], that is formed in a manner that allows for [[cut]]ting softer materials, especially meat or other food. There is often a point for piercing or stabbing.
# A [[weapon]] designed with the aforementioned specifications intended for [[slash]]ing and/or [[stab]]bing and too short to be called a sword. A [[dagger]].

